parameters:
『Mama』: Is this child... 'Alice'...? Don't say such
presumptuous things! There's no way that's true!! She's
my... precious 'daughter'!!

'Mama': You have no right to take away our 'happiness'!
Don't come near...! Don't get close to my 'daughter'!!

So this is the 'Alice' this time... To think that she was
even born from a 'counterfeit'... Truly, a terrifying
existence.

What should we do with 'this'? Should we handle it as
usual...?

Ah, send her to the disposal site. At this stage, she can't
survive outside. ...Smash her.
